description:
Twi Chang was a member of the Black Order and the former Head of http://anidb.net/ch32500 [Asian Branch] and Chang clan. She is Edgar Chang Martin`s wife, Bak Chang`s mother, and http://anidb.net/ch84703 [Zuu Mei Chang]`s niece, and was also the overseer of the Second Exorcist Project.
Source: D.Gray-man Wiki
name: Twi Chang
